competition_summary.context: Competition - We compete for natural gas and NGL supply with other midstream companies, major integrated oil companies and independent exploration and production companies that have gathering and processing assets, fractionators, intrastate and interstate pipelines and storage facilities.  The factors that typically affect our ability to compete for natural gas and NGL supply are: • quality of services provided; • producer drilling activity; • proceeds remitted and/or fees charged under our cont
